# game/anna1.rpy:29
translate Korean anna1_d2dc5415:

    # c "(She told me to meet her here, so she's got to be around somewhere.)"
    c "(여기서 만나자고 했지, 여기 어딘가 있을 거야.)"

# game/anna1.rpy:30
translate Korean anna1_8d584416:

    # m "The production facility had many different wings, covering everything from research to processing, in addition to production. It was easy to get lost if you didn't know where you were going."
    m "공장에는 생산 외에도 연구부터 가공까지, 모든 것을 관장하는 시설들이 많았다. 어디를 가는 지 모르고 길을 잃기 쉬웠다."

# game/anna1.rpy:36
translate Korean anna1_b230ba57:

    # m "I heard some commotion in the distance, and when I approached, I was surprised to see not only Anna, but Remy as well."
    m "멀리서 소란스러운 소리가 들려서, 그 곳에 가봤더니, 안나 뿐만 아니라 레미 또한 있었다."

# game/anna1.rpy:37
translate Korean anna1_64333f1a:

    # m "They seemed to be in the middle of a heated conversation. I thought it would be inappropriate to approach now, so I remained several paces back, out of their field of vision, but still close enough to be able to make out their words."
    m "그들은 한창 열이 올라 대화를 나누고 있었다. 지금 끼어들기엔 좀 그래서 그들이 나를 보지 못하도록 멀리서 대화만 들었다."

# game/anna1.rpy:42
translate Korean anna1_6a221be0:

    # Ry "We have heard the rumors."
    Ry "이미 소문은 듣고 왔습니다."

# game/anna1.rpy:46
translate Korean anna1_a17387cd:

    # An "So you come to me on the basis of rumors? Is that how you operate? What do you want from me?"
    An "그래서 소문만 듣고 저를 찾아오신거에요? 그딴 식으로 할 겁니까? 뭘 원하시는데요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:47
translate Korean anna1_3f4546f9:

    # Ry "This is not the first time you've been in trouble, you know. They might not be so lenient with you this time."
    Ry "아시다시피 이번 한 번만이 아니잖습니까. 이번에는 당신을 곱게 보지 않을 수도 있어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:51
translate Korean anna1_5e3528a3:

    # An "I don't know what you are talking about."
    An "뭘 말씀하시는 지 모르겠군요."

# game/anna1.rpy:52
translate Korean anna1_cc16093b:

    # Ry "Consider this a warning. You should proceed carefully, for your own good."
    Ry "이건 경고입니다. 당신을 위해서라도, 조심히 행동하셔야할 거에요."

# game/anna1.rpy:56
translate Korean anna1_4dc4a125:

    # An "If you wanted to threaten me, the least you could have done was to send someone more intimidating. You may be larger than I am, but even I can see that you're just a big coward. You wouldn't dare to put your dirty claws on me."
    An "절 협박하고 싶으신 거라면, 적어도 당신보다 더 위협적인 사람을 보내셨어야죠. 그 쪽이 저보다 크긴 하지만, 제 눈에는 그냥 거대한 얼간이 밖에 보이지 않네요. 감히 그 더러운 발톱을 제게 가져다대지도 못할거구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:60
translate Korean anna1_3a3d127a:

    # Ry "I wouldn't. I'm here as a courtesy to you, not to threaten or intimidate. Do with that information whatever you wish."
    Ry "그럴 생각 없습니다. 전 협박이 아니라 당신이 걱정되서 온 겁니다. 꼭 염두에 두시고 행동하세요."

# game/anna1.rpy:64
translate Korean anna1_df29eec3:

    # Ry "You know we'll be back, and if they find anything, there will be consequences."
    Ry "당신도 우리가 다시 올 거란 건 알고 계시잖아요. 게다가 그들이 뭐라도 찾으면, 결론날 테고요."

# game/anna1.rpy:65
translate Korean anna1_7ee0481f:

    # An "Do you think I care?"
    An "제가 신경쓸거라 생각하시는건가요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:69
translate Korean anna1_16a8a491:

    # Ry "This attitude of yours is not helpful."
    Ry "이런 태도는 도움이 되지 않을거에요."

# game/anna1.rpy:73
translate Korean anna1_ccbd7537:

    # An "Neither are you."
    An "그건 그 쪽도 마찬가지고요."

# game/anna1.rpy:77
translate Korean anna1_e9fe9500:

    # Ry "Well, I've said what I came here to say. Good luck."
    Ry "그럼, 어쨌거나 전 말씀드렸습니다. 행운을 빕니다."

# game/anna1.rpy:81
translate Korean anna1_32b2cfd8:

    # An "Whatever."
    An "그러거나 말거나."

# game/anna1.rpy:87
translate Korean anna1_28d33d90:

    # m "Remy turned to leave and started walking in my direction. I ducked behind a pillar, and when he went past, I wasn't sure if he'd seen me. Either way, he left, and I was safe to approach now."
    m "레미는 내 쪽으로 몸을 돌려 떠나려했다. 나는 그가 지나갈 때까지 몸을 기둥 뒤에 숨겼다. 그가 날 보았는 지는 확실하지 않지만, 어쨌거나 그는 갔고, 나는 안전하게 접근할 수 있었다."

# game/anna1.rpy:111
translate Korean anna1_0ff5f677:

    # s "My records indicate you have already experienced this scene in a satisfactory manner. Would you like to skip to the end?"
    s "My records indicate you have already experienced this scene in a satisfactory manner. Would you like to skip to the end?"

# game/anna1.rpy:119
translate Korean anna1_eee83226:

    # s "It looks like you've seen this before. Skip to the end of this scene?"
    s "It looks like you've seen this before. Skip to the end of this scene?"

# game/anna1.rpy:127
translate Korean anna1_e7709aa0:

    # s "So, it turns out you've seen this before. Either you could watch this again, or we could save some time and just skip to the end of this scene."
    s "So, it turns out you've seen this before. Either you could watch this again, or we could save some time and just skip to the end of this scene."

