# game/anna1.rpy:175
translate Korean anna1_15b4d010:

    # An "Who cares?"
    An "알 게 뭐에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:181
translate Korean anna1_206a6186:

    # An "Hey, [player_name]."
    An "반갑네요, [player_name]씨."

# game/anna1.rpy:186
translate Korean anna1_e8ba533a:

    # An "Hey."
    An "반가워요."

# game/anna1.rpy:190
translate Korean anna1_1b46c468:

    # An "Wait, how long have you been here?"
    An "잠깐, 언제부터 여기 있던거에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:202
translate Korean anna1_baa3667a:

    # An "Not that it matters much anyway. This is just par for the course for me."
    An "아무튼 그건 더 이상 중요치않아요. 나한텐 당연한 일이니까."

# game/anna1.rpy:203
translate Korean anna1_479e6953:

    # c "I know Remy. What's the problem?"
    c "전 레미를 알아요. 뭐가 문제에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:207
translate Korean anna1_5a61a232:

    # An "The nerve of that guy. He probably wouldn't be so uptight if it wasn't for that thing with his girlfriend a few years ago."
    An "저 남정네의 불안이요. 몇 년 전에 여자친구와 그런 일만 없었더라면 이렇게 빡빡하게 굴진 않았을 것을."

# game/anna1.rpy:211
translate Korean anna1_93f35ab2:

    # An "But I don't care about him. It's his superiors that are the problem. They don't like me and the research I'm doing. They cite their traditions and values, claiming that those are what have kept us alive for so long."
    An "하지만 전 신경쓰지 않아요. 문제는 그의 윗대가리들이지. 그들은 제가 하고 있는 연구가 마음에 들지 않나봐요. 전통과 가치를 운운하면서 그것들이 우리를 오랫동안 살아남게 해준 것이라 주장하거든요."

# game/anna1.rpy:215
translate Korean anna1_fd0e7feb:

    # An "If anything were to change, it would obviously fracture the base this society is built on, cause it all to collapse, tear apart families and allow all hell to break loose."
    An "어느 것이라도 바뀌게 된다면, 그 변화는 사회의 구조를 망가트려서, 모든 걸 붕괴할 것이고, 가족을 분단시킬 것이며, 모두에게 지옥을 선사하겠죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:219
translate Korean anna1_36b5bba3:

    # An "At least if you believe those old-timers who keep repeating these phrases."
    An "적어도 당신이 이런 같은 말만 반복하는 노친네들을 믿는다면요."

# game/anna1.rpy:223
translate Korean anna1_54f42344:

    # An "And all that nonsense, because of my research. Valuable research that could save lives, mind you."
    An "그리고 내 연구 때문이라는 그 모든 허튼소리들. 장담하건데, 그건 생명을 구할 가치 있는 연구라구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:224
translate Korean anna1_981a8a46:

    # c "What kind of research are we talking about?"
    c "무슨 연구를 말씀하시는 건가요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:228
translate Korean anna1_7194792c:

    # An "I could show you sometime, but we're here to have fun, right?"
    An "그건 언제라도 알려드릴 수 있겠지만, 지금은 놀러온 거 맞죠?"

# game/anna1.rpy:229
translate Korean anna1_ec71e0ee:

    # c "I thought you wanted to show me, since you said we were both in biology and all that."
    c "저는 우리 둘다 생물학 쪽에 있으니 저한테 보여주고 싶으신 줄 알았는데요."

# game/anna1.rpy:231
translate Korean anna1_4e54941b:

    # An "Sure, but after doing this all day, you'll have to excuse me for not wanting to talk about it even more."
    An "아, 물론이죠, 하지만 그런 걸 하루종일 했다가는, 그런 소리를 더 이상 듣기 싫다며 애원해야할 걸요."

# game/anna1.rpy:235
translate Korean anna1_501d818b:

    # An "Wasting my time with that guy was just another setback, not that I don't already have more than enough work to do. Even right now I'm supposed to be working overtime."
    An "그 남자와 시간을 낭비하는 건 그저 약간의 차질일 뿐이지, 제가 할 일이 없다는 건 아니거든요. 오늘도 잔업이 있어서요."

# game/anna1.rpy:247
translate Korean anna1_206a6186_1:

    # An "Hey, [player_name]."
    An "반갑네요, [player_name]씨."

# game/anna1.rpy:252
translate Korean anna1_e8ba533a_1:

    # An "Hey."
    An "반가워요."

# game/anna1.rpy:254
translate Korean anna1_3501252f:

    # c "Is something wrong? You don't look great."
    c "뭐 문제라도 있으세요? 썩 좋아보이시진 않네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:258
translate Korean anna1_781a7e53:

    # An "It's nothing, really. Just the usual stress that comes with the job. Even right now I'm supposed to be working overtime."
    An "아무 것도 아니에요. 그냥 직장 스트레스에요. 오늘도 잔업이 있어서 말이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:260
translate Korean anna1_afb05e33:

    # c "I see. What do you actually do here?"
    c "알았어요. 여기서 정확히 뭘 하시는 건가요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:264
translate Korean anna1_7194792c_1:

    # An "I could show you sometime, but we're here to have fun, right?"
    An "그건 언제라도 알려드릴 수 있겠지만, 지금은 놀러온 거 맞죠?"

# game/anna1.rpy:266
translate Korean anna1_ec71e0ee_1:

    # c "I thought you wanted to show me, since you said we were both in biology and all that."
    c "저는 우리 둘다 생물학 쪽에 있으니 저한테 보여주고 싶으신 줄 알았는데요."

# game/anna1.rpy:270
translate Korean anna1_4e54941b_1:

    # An "Sure, but after doing this all day, you'll have to excuse me for not wanting to talk about it even more."
    An "아, 물론이죠, 하지만 그런 걸 하루종일 했다가는, 그런 소리를 더 이상 듣기 싫다며 애원해야할 걸요."

# game/anna1.rpy:278
translate Korean anna1_09070b4b:

    # An "I will."
    An "그러겠죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:284
translate Korean anna1_88e9b9fb:

    # An "Yeah, I'm very sorry we can't accommodate your request right now, your highness."
    An "예, 정말 송구스럽지만 지금 당장 당신의 요청을 들어드릴 수 없겠군요, 폐하."

# game/anna1.rpy:291
translate Korean anna1_809161f6:

    # An "Good to know we see eye to eye on this."
    An "서로 의견이 맞아 다행이네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:294
translate Korean anna1_dc820742:

    # An "Oh, and thanks for the blood, by the way. The results aren't in yet, but I'll let you know when they are."
    An "아, 그나저나 혈액 샘플은 고마워요. 결과는 아직 안나왔지만, 나오게 되면 바로 알려드리죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:295
translate Korean anna1_3133c34e:

    # c "Good. I'm just as curious about the results as you are."
    c "네. 저도 결과가 궁금하던 참이었어요. 당신만큼요."

# game/anna1.rpy:297
translate Korean anna1_9a462ada:

    # An "No, you aren't."
    An "아니죠, 저만큼은 아닐걸요."

# game/anna1.rpy:298
translate Korean anna1_0a0912e4:

    # c "I am. I am way curiouser than you are."
    c "맞을걸요. 전 당신보다 더 요상한 사람이거든요."

# game/anna1.rpy:300
translate Korean anna1_9f1aeeac:

    # An "Curiouser? Is that even a word?"
    An "요상하다? 그거 단어는 맞아요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:301
translate Korean anna1_e3109ce5:

    # c "It is, since an author popularized its use where I came from."
    c "맞아요, 제가 살던 곳에서 작가가 대중화시켰죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:303
translate Korean anna1_d14a6516:

    # An "Then I am way more curiouser than you are."
    An "그럼 당신보다 제가 더 요상한 사람이에요."

# game/anna1.rpy:304
translate Korean anna1_65ce626d:

    # c "Not if I am the curiousest."
    c "제가 요상자가 아니었다면 말이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:306
translate Korean anna1_3f4c75b3:

    # An "Excuse me for a moment, but I must weep for the English language. At this rate, why don't you just say you're the \"most curiouserest\"?"
    An "잠깐만요, 영어라는 언어를 위해 눈물을 흘릴 수 밖에 없겠네요. 방금 왜 \"가장 요상한 사람\"이라고 하지를 않은 거에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:307
translate Korean anna1_ad12b171:

    # c "I'm not sure, I am not a linguist. Are you?"
    c "그건 잘 모르겠네요. 전 언어학자가 아니라서요. 당신은요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:309
translate Korean anna1_aa1f612c:

    # An "Not exactly, but I have a way with words. My tongue is quite skilled, or so I hear."
    An "그렇지는 않지만, 말솜씨가 좋긴 하거든요. 제 입이 날래다던지, 그렇게 말하곤 해요."

# game/anna1.rpy:311
translate Korean anna1_145bfa91:

    # An "Some might even say \"cunning\"."
    An "일부는 \"교활하다\"고까지 하죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:317
translate Korean anna1_84a1d6ad:

    # c "In any case, if you have to work overtime today, does that mean I should wait for you, or do you want me to come back another time?"
    c "아무튼, 오늘 잔업이 있다 하셨으니, 제가 기다릴까요? 아니면 다른 때에 찾아뵐까요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:318
translate Korean anna1_d1affb50:

    # An "Neither, I think my break should start right about... now."
    An "둘 다 아니에요. 휴식 시간이 시작됐거든요... 지금 막 말이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:325
translate Korean anna1_a0184477:

    # An "It is, isn't it?"
    An "확실히 그렇죠?"

# game/anna1.rpy:332
translate Korean anna1_8a39980d:

    # An "As long as you don't rat me out, that shouldn't be a problem."
    An "절 밀고한다거나 그러지만 않으면 문제는 없을 거에요."

# game/anna1.rpy:336
translate Korean anna1_63b615c0:

    # An "Just one of the perks of being the manager of this facility."
    An "이 시설의 관리자만이 가질 수 있는 특권 중 하나죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:338
translate Korean anna1_8b0c65b1:

    # c "So, where are we going?"
    c "그래서, 어디로 갈까요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:342
translate Korean anna1_073c8a43:

    # An "I don't know where you are going, but I think I need a coffee or five. You can tag along if you like."
    An "당신이 어디로 갈 진 모르겠지만, 일단 커피가 다섯 잔 정도는 필요하겠네요. 원하시면 따라가드릴게요."

# game/anna1.rpy:349
translate Korean anna1_2b65165b:

    # An "We'll see if it'll be mine as well."
    An "감사하셔야할지 한 번 두고보자고요."

# game/anna1.rpy:354
translate Korean anna1_16f4549a:

    # An "Suit yourself."
    An "좋을대로 하세요."

# game/anna1.rpy:359
translate Korean anna1_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/anna1.rpy:362
translate Korean anna1_a1018474:

    # n "Whatever the reason, I decided not to join her in her glorious quest for coffee."
    n "이유야 어찌됐건, 난 그녀의 커피 탐색에 참가하지 않기로 했다."

# game/anna1.rpy:363
translate Korean anna1_3a948282:

    # n "I wasn't sure whether I would regret the choice I made in the times to come, but in the end, it is what I had to do."
    n "시간이 흐르며 내 선택을 후회하게 될 지는 확신할 수 없었지만, 결국은, 후회하게 되었다."

# game/anna1.rpy:389
translate Korean anna1_0c82e1c2:

    # An "Now that's a convincing reason."
    An "왜인지는 아실 거라 믿어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:392
translate Korean anna1_b0cff734:

    # An "I hope you brought your own money, though, because I'm not sharing."
    An "지갑은 챙겨오셨길 빌어요, 제가 사드리진 않을 생각이거든요."

# game/anna1.rpy:393
translate Korean anna1_526c91f6:

    # c "I didn't, but everything I purchase is taken care of by my ambassador status."
    c "가지고 오진 않았는데, 제가 대사다 보니 뭐든지 살 수 있겠죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:397
translate Korean anna1_7642647c:

    # An "Nice. Actually, that opens up some very interesting possibilities."
    An "좋아요. 사실, 그렇게 말씀하시니 몇몇 가능성이 떠오르네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:398
translate Korean anna1_5554047b:

    # c "It might, but I'd rather not do anything too fishy. I don't want to raise any suspicion, you know."
    c "그러겠지만, 전 딱히 수상쩍은 짓은 하고 싶지 않네요. 아시다시피 전 괜한 의심은 사기 싫거든요."

# game/anna1.rpy:402
translate Korean anna1_5057e9fb:

    # An "Good point."
    An "좋은 지적이에요."

# game/anna1.rpy:406
translate Korean anna1_37acbaf0:

    # An "Well, let's go then."
    An "그럼, 가도록 하죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:408
translate Korean anna1_1274b54e:

    # c "After you, milady."
    c "먼저 가시죠, 마님."

# game/anna1.rpy:420
translate Korean anna1_fd94623d:

    # c "There we are."
    c "도착했네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:427
translate Korean anna1_db180c37:

    # An "Finally. I can't wait to get some coffee into my system."
    An "마침내요. 제 몸에 커피를 빨리 넣어주고 싶네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:431
translate Korean anna1_692a2e32:

    # Ad "Oh, hello [player_name]. Nice to see you again."
    Ad "아, 안녕하세요 [player_name]씨. 다시 뵙네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:432
translate Korean anna1_6190f4db:

    # c "Hey."
    c "안녕하세요."

# game/anna1.rpy:433
translate Korean anna1_5d6ec4e1:

    # Ad "Who's your companion?"
    Ad "같이 오신 분은 누구신가요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:437
translate Korean anna1_9971e8f6:

    # An "Can't you just take my order?"
    An "그냥 주문이나 받으시죠?"

# game/anna1.rpy:441
translate Korean anna1_c97a6805:

    # Ad "I apologize. Let me try that again."
    Ad "죄송해요. 그러면 다시 할게요."

# game/anna1.rpy:447
translate Korean anna1_beab5379:

    # Ad "Welcome to our establishment. My name's Adine, and I'll be your waitress today. What can I bring you two?"
    Ad "어서오세요. 저는 아디네라고 한답니다. 주문 받을게요, 두 분 어떤 걸 가져다드릴까요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:449
translate Korean anna1_24bf5684:

    # An "I'll have a coffee."
    An "커피 한 잔이요."

# game/anna1.rpy:453
translate Korean anna1_9d9d1b9a:

    # Ad "Thank you. And what can I bring the esteemed gentleperson on the other side of the table?"
    Ad "알겠습니다. 그러면 반대쪽에 젠틀한 신사분께는 뭘 가져다드릴까요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:468
translate Korean anna1_8d408356:

    # Ad "No problem, I'll be right back."
    Ad "알겠습니다, 곧 가져다드릴게요."

# game/anna1.rpy:476
translate Korean anna1_e2d0e6cd:

    # An "What's her problem? I'm here to order something, not to chit-chat with the employees."
    An "그 여자 뭐가 문제인 걸까요? 전 여기 주문하러 온 거지 직원이랑 잡담이나 하러 온 게 아닌데 말이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:482
translate Korean anna1_e017146f:

    # An "I guess I'm not a fan of \"friendly\", then."
    An "그럼 전 \"친절\"과는 거리가 먼 것 같군요."

# game/anna1.rpy:489
translate Korean anna1_84acc050:

    # An "If you say so."
    An "그렇게 말씀하신다면야."

# game/anna1.rpy:495
translate Korean anna1_d2227b0e:

    # An "I can see that."
    An "저도 그렇게 생각해요."

# game/anna1.rpy:502
translate Korean anna1_8179bfe4:

    # Ad "Here you go. Enjoy."
    Ad "여깄습니다, 맛있게 드세요."

# game/anna1.rpy:519
translate Korean anna1_d1a103e3:

    # An "Ah, I totally needed that."
    An "아, 이게 필요했어."

# game/anna1.rpy:520
translate Korean anna1_b08c600f:

    # c "So, you work in that facility."
    c "그래서, 당신이 그 시설에서 일하신다 했죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:521
translate Korean anna1_5343140e:

    # An "And your point is?"
    An "그래서 요점은요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:522
translate Korean anna1_3a37edec:

    # c "What's your job there? I mean, what do you do, exactly?"
    c "거기서 무슨 역할을 하시는 거에요? 그러니까, 정확히 뭘 하시죠?"

# game/anna1.rpy:523
translate Korean anna1_351663c1:

    # An "We do all kinds of things. The truth is, we just have all kinds of specialized machinery there which is used by many different people for many different purposes. The building is owned and run by the council, who oversees the schedule."
    An "사실상 모든 종류의 일을 다 해요. 사실, 많은 사람들이 각기 다른 목적으로 사용할 수 있게끔 모든 종류의 특수 기계들이 있죠. 건물은 의회 소유인데, 의회가 일정을 관리하죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:527
translate Korean anna1_6cb0e058:

    # An "It is quite handy, since you can go from research, to testing and even manufacturing, all in the same complex."
    An "연구나, 실험이나, 게다가 제조까지 모두 같은 시설에 있으니까 확실히 꽤 편해요."

# game/anna1.rpy:531
translate Korean anna1_f05dd5e5:

    # An "I started out as a researcher in biology, which is still my main job, but I've been there so long and learned the ins and outs of the building so well that eventually I was asked to take over some managerial duties."
    An "저는 본업인 생물학자로서 시작했지만, 오랫동안 그 시설에 있으면서 건물의 내외사정을 잘 알게되니까, 결국 관리 업무 중 일부를 맡아달라는 제안을 받았죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:532
translate Korean anna1_71fb7109:

    # An "Sure, it means more work, but it also allows me to run a personal project every once in a while. Does that sate your curiosity?"
    An "물론, 업무가 더 많아지겠지만, 제 개인적인 프로젝트도 실행할 수 있다는 것이겠죠. 이제 궁금증이 해결되셨나요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:539
translate Korean anna1_824f6a3f:

    # An "I'm not sure I'd go so far as to call it \"fascinating\", but it surely does give me a lot of opportunities."
    An "그걸 \"매력적이다\"라고 까지 불러야할진 모르겠지만, 확실히 제게 많은 기회를 주긴 했죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:543
translate Korean anna1_0b08fe43:

    # An "Good to know."
    An "다행이네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:549
translate Korean anna1_ee139601:

    # An "Well, that's a shame."
    An "뭐, 유감스럽네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:553
translate Korean anna1_72418553:

    # c "Oh, I forgot to ask you what you actually planned to do with my blood and the test results."
    c "아, 제 혈액으로 정확히 뭘 하고 결과를 언제 내실 계획인지 물어보는 걸 깜빡했네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:556
translate Korean anna1_4e9eabf5:

    # c "Out of more curiosity, when you asked me about my blood the other day, what were you actually planning on doing with it?"
    c "더 궁금한 게 있는데, 그 날 제 혈액에 대해 물어보셨을 때, 그걸로 뭘 하실 생각이셨어요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:560
translate Korean anna1_01a15273:

    # An "What is this, an interrogation?"
    An "그건 뭐, 심문이에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:565
translate Korean anna1_4cad5cfe:

    # An "Well, it's not the first."
    An "글쎄요, 이게 처음은 아니거든요."

# game/anna1.rpy:571
translate Korean anna1_7318a035:

    # An "Maybe I should. I'll tell her you hit me, then sue for damages."
    An "그래야할 것 같네요. 당신이 날 때렸다고 하고, 손해배상 소송이라고 걸어봐야겠어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:576
translate Korean anna1_169504fd:

    # An "Then you must be talking about Adine, the prying waitress, or yourself, because you haven't seen me in a bad mood yet. Not even close."
    An "계속 뭔가를 캐묻는 아디네를 말하는 건가요, 아니면 당신 자신을 말씀하시는 건가요? 제가 기분이 나쁠 때를 보지 않으셨으니까요. 지금은 나쁜 기색조차도 없고."

# game/anna1.rpy:590
translate Korean anna1_cbd94a65:

    # An "..."
    An "..."

# game/anna1.rpy:594
translate Korean anna1_7d8ee730:

    # An "Sorry, I'm just stressed from all the work lately. I'm not getting much respite between my regular work, overtime, personal projects and other disturbances like that Remy sticking his nose where it doesn't belong."
    An "미안해요, 늦게까지 일하느라 스트레스가 좀 쌓였거든요. 별로 휴식 시간이 없어요. 정규적인 업무, 초과 근무에, 개인적인 프로젝트, 거기에 레미가 오지랖을 부리는 방해까지 있으니까요."

# game/anna1.rpy:595
translate Korean anna1_9e671d0d:

    # c "What do you usually do during your free time? Having a good work-life balance is very important, you know."
    c "여가 시간에는 주로 뭘 하시는데요? 아시다시피 워라벨은 중요하잖아요."

# game/anna1.rpy:596
translate Korean anna1_f3734192:

    # An "I love my job, I really do. Actually, I love it so much that even in my free time, I still do things that have to do with biology."
    An "전 제 직업이 좋아요, 정말로요. 사실, 제 여가 시간에조차 생물학에 관련된 일이라면 뭐든 할 정도로 너무 좋아해요."

# game/anna1.rpy:597
translate Korean anna1_a9f2c31d:

    # An "As I said, I've got the opportunity to do my own projects sometimes, so that's what I focus on when I get the chance. It would be a shame to pass up an opportunity like that without using it."
    An "제가 말했듯이 제 개인적인 프로젝트를 할 기회가 생겨서, 단지 기회가 찾아왔을 때 최대한 투자하는 것 뿐이에요. 기회가 왔을 때 이용하지 않는 건 어리석은 일이니까요."

# game/anna1.rpy:598
translate Korean anna1_5a3ffb68:

    # An "With the current influx of work, I rarely leave the facility if I'm not eating or sleeping. Even right now, I'm only on break and have to go back for another shift."
    An "요즘처럼 일이 몰릴 때는 밥과 잠을 제외하고 시설을 떠날 일이 없어요. 지금조차도 휴식 시간일 뿐이지 곧 다시 근무하러 돌아가야하죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:599
translate Korean anna1_aacef7dd:

    # c "Maybe you should do something else for a change."
    c "변화를 위해 다른 뭔가를 해보셔야 할 것 같아요."

# game/anna1.rpy:603
translate Korean anna1_0c61b9b0:

    # An "Maybe, but right now that's not really an option. It would help if the council weren't constantly sending their lackeys to mess with me."
    An "그래야겠죠, 하지만 지금은 선택할 수 있는 상황이 아니라서요. 의회가 계속 하인들을 보내지 않으면 도움이 될 것 같지만."

# game/anna1.rpy:604
translate Korean anna1_9bc48217:

    # c "So that wasn't the first time?"
    c "그래서 그게 처음이 아니었단 거에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:608
translate Korean anna1_ab057f7c:

    # An "No, I suppose I'm on their watchlist or something."
    An "네. 제가 뭐 감시 대상자 리스트에라도 등재되어있나 보죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:609
translate Korean anna1_1bc47770:

    # c "Why is that?"
    c "왜 그런거에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:610
translate Korean anna1_4a974f6e:

    # An "It's a long story. And not one for a first date."
    An "아주 긴 이야기죠. 첫 데이트에 어울릴만한 이야기도 아니고요."

# game/anna1.rpy:611
translate Korean anna1_b1d7e26c:

    # c "So you're saying this is a date?"
    c "이게 데이트라는 거에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:615
translate Korean anna1_995f38ea:

    # An "No, I'm saying that even if this was a date, which would be more than whatever this is, it wouldn't be very appropriate. Stories about work aren't very romantic."
    An "아뇨, 이게 데이트, 아니 그 이상의 무언가였다고 하더라도, 별로 적절하지 않을 거라는 거죠. 딱히 아름답지도 않은 이야기거든요."

# game/anna1.rpy:616
translate Korean anna1_83cfd907:

    # c "It's always about work with you. Come on, you're on break. Maybe we should do something to take your mind off of all that for once."
    c "당신의 일에 관련된 거니까요. 지금은 휴식 시간이잖아요? 한 번만이라도 다른 데에다 마음을 둘 수 있는 뭔갈 해야하지 않겠어요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:620
translate Korean anna1_c7de8994:

    # An "Like what?"
    An "예를 들자면요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:621
translate Korean anna1_d009f7ee:

    # c "I'm not sure. Do you have any other hobbies?"
    c "전 잘 모르겠네요. 취미라도 있으세요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:622
translate Korean anna1_4d5202ea:

    # An "Not really."
    An "딱히 없어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:623
translate Korean anna1_1e0a2514:

    # c "Hey, waitress."
    c "여기요."

# game/anna1.rpy:629
translate Korean anna1_1195b284:

    # Ad "How can I help you?"
    Ad "뭘 도와드릴까요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:630
translate Korean anna1_33bb994f:

    # c "Do you have anything here to entertain your guests? Any games or other distractions?"
    c "뭐 손님들을 위해 준비두신 거라도 있으신가요? 게임이든 오락이든요."

# game/anna1.rpy:631
translate Korean anna1_6b6f7eca:

    # Ad "I'm not sure, let me go check."
    Ad "잘 모르겠어요, 확인해볼게요."

# game/anna1.rpy:638
translate Korean anna1_5877796a:

    # An "What exactly are you trying to do?"
    An "정확히 뭘 하시려는 거에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:645
translate Korean anna1_32b2cfd8_1:

    # An "Whatever."
    An "그러던지 말던지."

# game/anna1.rpy:648
translate Korean anna1_6e60f766:

    # An "The anticipation is killing me."
    An "기대감이 절 지치게 하네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:650
translate Korean anna1_f14b961c:

    # An "Actually, no. It's boredom."
    An "아니지, 아니야. 이건 지루함이네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:656
translate Korean anna1_9b2d911e:

    # An "I'll remember this day. For good or bad, I'm not sure yet."
    An "이 날이 기억에 남겠네요. 좋은 의미로든, 나쁜 의미로든. 아직 확실치는 않아요."

# game/anna1.rpy:662
translate Korean anna1_7a1c70a3:

    # Ad "It's more for the kids, but we don't really have anything else."
    Ad "아이들을 위한 건 더 있지만, 이거 말고는 적당한 게 없는 것 같아요."

# game/anna1.rpy:668
translate Korean anna1_cf1a9d22:

    # c "It's fine, thank you."
    c "괜찮습니다, 고마워요."

# game/anna1.rpy:672
translate Korean anna1_6f9d05c4:

    # Ad "Have fun!"
    Ad "재밌게 즐기세요!"

# game/anna1.rpy:680
translate Korean anna1_c6a90608:

    # An "A board game? Really?"
    An "보드게임? 정말요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:681
translate Korean anna1_e658b925:

    # c "I know it's not Knizki's {i}Textile Merchant{/i}, but I suppose it's better than nothing."
    c "이게 크니즈키의 {i}Textile Merchant{/i}은 아니지만, 아무것도 하지 않는 것보다는 나을 거에요."

# game/anna1.rpy:685
translate Korean anna1_fa19e5d4:

    # An "{i}Textile Merchant{/i}? Knizki?"
    An "{i}Textile Merchant{/i}? 크니즈키?{i}(역: 영국드라마 \"IT Crowd\" 속 가상의 보드게임){/i}"

# game/anna1.rpy:686
translate Korean anna1_2e2553b3:

    # c "It's a game. Never mind."
    c "그냥 게임이에요. 신경쓰지 마세요."

# game/anna1.rpy:691
translate Korean anna1_d3f48fd2:

    # An "Well, I'm not convinced that this will accomplish anything, unless your goal is to make me regret this day."
    An "글쎄, 제가 오늘을 후회하도록 만들고 싶으신게 아니라면, 이게 해결해줄 거라고 확신할 수 없어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:692
translate Korean anna1_5b3a3cb1:

    # c "It seems to be a trivia game. Do you have good general knowledge?"
    c "상식퀴즈 게임 같네요. 상식 좋아하세요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:693
translate Korean anna1_91a94269:

    # An "Do you even know what kind of advanced knowledge I have to memorize and work with every single day?"
    An "제가 매일 전문적인 지식들을 암기해야한다는 건 알고 계세요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:697
translate Korean anna1_9714e430:

    # An "You bet I have good general knowledge. Certainly more than enough to beat a foreigner like you."
    An "제가 상식에는 뛰어나다는 걸 확신하시게 될 거에요. 특히나 당신같은 외지인 상대로는 말이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:698
translate Korean anna1_16cf313c:

    # c "If you're so confident, maybe we should make a bet."
    c "자신이 있으신가본데, 내기를 해보시는 건 어떤가요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:702
translate Korean anna1_5b4ed353:

    # An "What do you have in mind?"
    An "어떤 내기를 원하시는데요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:703
translate Korean anna1_8ecea63c:

    # c "Let's say if I win, I'll get to go on a real date with you."
    c "제가 이기면, 진짜 데이트를 해주시죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:704
translate Korean anna1_b95464b4:

    # c "No fitting me in during your break, no complaining about everything, and no acting as if you're doing me a favor, especially because it was you who wanted to meet me in the first place."
    c "당신의 휴식 시간에 굳이 저를 만나려하지 마시고, 모든 것에 불평하지 마시고, 마치 제게 호의를 베푸는 듯 행동하지마세요. 처음에 저를 만나고 싶다 한 건 당신이었으니까."

# game/anna1.rpy:708
translate Korean anna1_1be57190:

    # An "I'll have you come in sometime so I can run more tests on you."
    An "제가 이기면, 그 쪽을 대상으로 실험할 게 있으니 언제 한 번 당신을 부르도록 하죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:712
translate Korean anna1_73ed9de4:

    # An "And if I win, I'll have you come in sometime so I can run a few tests on you. I won't even need your blood anymore."
    An "제가 이기면, 그 쪽을 대상으로 실험할 게 있으니 언제 한 번 당신을 부르도록 하죠. 이젠 당신의 혈액도 필요 없어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:717
translate Korean anna1_95705c40:

    # An "Let's do this, then."
    An "그럼 하자구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:725
translate Korean anna1_4eb24f9d:

    # An "But that's the only thing I'm interested in. You were so cocky you made a bet, but when it comes down to it, I suppose you don't have it in you."
    An "하지만 제가 그 쪽에 관심있는 건 그것뿐인 걸요. 당신이 자만심에 빠져 먼저 승부를 걸어오셨는데, 막상 닥치니까 거실 게 없나보네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:730
translate Korean anna1_e8d0b893:

    # An "How disappointing. I guess this whole thing was just a waste of time, then."
    An "실망스럽군요. 그러면 이 모든 게 싹 다 시간 낭비였다는 거네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:732
translate Korean anna1_175760ef:

    # An "Maybe you should play your children's games with the waitress, because I've got better things to do."
    An "저 종업원이랑 애들이나 하는 게임이나 즐기세요. 전 따로 해야할 일이 있어서 말이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:739
translate Korean anna1_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/anna1.rpy:742
translate Korean anna1_1263240e:

    # n "She simply got up and left without looking back even once."
    n "그녀는 일어서 뒤도 돌아보지 않고 자리를 떠났다."

# game/anna1.rpy:743
translate Korean anna1_559bef36:

    # n "And she didn't pay for her coffee, either."
    n "게다가 커피 값도 내지 않았다."

# game/anna1.rpy:744
translate Korean anna1_e61b5c67:

    # n "She probably hadn't forgotten, but whether she just didn't care, or if it was her way of sticking it to me, I wasn't sure."
    n "잊어버린 건 아니었겠지만, 단지 그녀가 신경쓰지 않았던 것 뿐인지, 내게 고집을 부리는 그녀만의 방식인지, 확실하지 않았다."

# game/anna1.rpy:745
translate Korean anna1_4fa19515:

    # n "I was quite sure, however, that she probably would not want to meet with me again."
    n "하지만 그녀가 나와 다시 만나지 않을 거란 것 만큼은 확신할 수 있었다."

# game/anna1.rpy:771
translate Korean anna1_95705c40_1:

    # An "Let's do this, then."
    An "그럼 해볼까요."

# game/anna1.rpy:775
translate Korean anna1_89cbbcd7:

    # An "Since it was your idea, it's only fair that I start. So, how does this work?"
    An "당신 아이디어니까, 제가 시작하는 게 공평하겠죠. 그래서, 어떻게 하는거죠?"

# game/anna1.rpy:776
translate Korean anna1_8fb95eeb:

    # c "It seems to be pretty simple. We take turns drawing cards and asking questions until we've both asked a number that we agree on beforehand. Whoever gets more right in the end wins."
    c "꽤 간단해보이네요. 먼저 정한 "

# game/anna1.rpy:777
translate Korean anna1_292b41ad:

    # An "How many questions shall it be, then?"
    An "그러면 질문은 몇 개로 하시겠어요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:778
translate Korean anna1_a41d7d3e:

    # c "How about five?"
    c "다섯 개 어떤가요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:779
translate Korean anna1_0b40c3cf:

    # An "Let's make it three. Not sure how long this will take, and my break won't be for too long, either."
    An "세 개로 하죠. 얼마나 걸릴 지도 모르고, 제 휴식 시간이 그리 길 것 같지 않거든요."

# game/anna1.rpy:780
translate Korean anna1_4137e81a:

    # c "Alright. Go ahead, then."
    c "좋습니다. 먼저 하시죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:784
translate Korean anna1_3a429c00:

    # m "I saw mischief in her eyes, her stare piercing, paired with the hint of an arrogant smirk that exposed her anticipation. She seemed confident that she would win and loved every second of it."
    m "그녀의 눈에서 장난기 어린 눈빛이 나왔고, 그녀의 입가에선 자신이 이길 것이라는 오만함에 가득찬 미소가 보였다. 그녀는 이길 자신으로 가득 차 있었고 매 순간순간을 즐기고 있는 듯 했다."

# game/anna1.rpy:785
translate Korean anna1_3c8056a2:

    # m "Slowly, her hand went over to the deck of cards and drew the topmost."
    m "그녀는 손을 천천히 카드 뭉치로 가져가 가장 위쪽에 놓여있는 카드를 뽑았다."

# game/anna1.rpy:801
translate Korean anna1_8dd493bd:

    # An "Who is cited as one of our most important historians, his work spanning over 20 books, credited with mapping out our entire history since the beginning of sentience?"
    An "가장 영향력있는 역사학자 중 한 명으로 손에 꼽히는 사람은 누구인가? 그는 20권 이상의 책을 집필했고, 기록이 시작된 이래로 모든 역사를 정리한 것으로 인정받고 있다."

# game/anna1.rpy:808
translate Korean anna1_2fa2fb8c:

    # An "How could you even know something like that? You have only been here for what, a few days?"
    An "어떻게 알고 계신거에요? 그러니까, 당신은 여기에 며칠동안만 머무르지 않았나요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:814
translate Korean anna1_900ba916:

    # An "Maybe."
    An "그런 것 같네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:821
translate Korean anna1_0e088460:

    # An "You won't be so lucky again."
    An "이번엔 그렇게 못 할걸요."

# game/anna1.rpy:827
translate Korean anna1_4bf8a8dc:

    # An "Let's see if you can keep it up."
    An "어디 그 기세 유지할 수 있을 지 두고보자구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:840
translate Korean wrong1_4f886a3e:

    # An "I'm afraid that's wrong. I'm so sorry, [player_name]."
    An "아쉽지만 아니에요. 유감이네요, [player_name]씨."

# game/anna1.rpy:841
translate Korean wrong1_8e5310b3:

    # c "How was I supposed to know something like that?"
    c "제가 어떻게 그런 걸 알겠어요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:843
translate Korean wrong1_e34af289:

    # An "It was your challenge. You dig your grave, you lie in it."
    An "당신이 도전한 거 잖아요. 무덤을 판 건 당신이고, 거기에 누운 것도 당신이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:844
translate Korean wrong1_d0b80300:

    # An "Besides, it's not as if it wasn't clear to me from the beginning that I'd win, so no surprises there."
    An "게다가, 애초에 당신이 절 이길 수 있을 것 같지도 않았으니까, 놀라울 건 없죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:849
translate Korean cont1_b3f8bf41:

    # c "Let's see how you fare with your first question."
    c "그럼 당신은 첫 번째 질문에 얼마나 잘 대답하시는지 볼까요."

# game/anna1.rpy:851
translate Korean cont1_c0e353ca:

    # An "Bring it."
    An "해보세요."

# game/anna1.rpy:857
translate Korean cont1_e7d505dd:

    # c "How far can you walk into the woods?"
    c "숲 속으로 얼마나 멀리 걸어갈 수 있는가?"

# game/anna1.rpy:858
translate Korean cont1_f67814b1:

    # An "Only until the middle. Anything after that and you're walking out of the woods again."
    An "중간까지만. 그 이상을 가게되면 그건 숲 속으로 들어가는 게 아닌 빠져나오는 거니까."

# game/anna1.rpy:859
translate Korean cont1_46db7d15:

    # c "You're right. That's a rather weird question, though."
    c "정답이에요. 좀 이상한 질문이네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:862
translate Korean cont1_9645f5aa:

    # An "I suppose I read the right kinds of books growing up. I know most of those trick questions."
    An "어렸을 때 그런 종류의 책을 읽어봤던 것 같네요. 그런 속임수들은 제가 잘 알죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:866
translate Korean cont1_932eddc4:

    # An "Let's see what the second question has in store for you, shall we?"
    An "그러면 두번째 질문을 한 번 꺼내볼까요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:886
translate Korean cont1_d66fe21d:

    # An "Alright, if there are five apples and you take away three, how many do you have?"
    An "좋아요, 사과 다섯 개에서 당신이 세 개를 가져가면, 당신에겐 몇 개가 남죠?"

# game/anna1.rpy:898
translate Korean cont1_bfc11f19:

    # An "Guess you also know your trick questions."
    An "당신도 이런 질문들을 잘 아시는 것 같네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:899
translate Korean cont1_5a04b24f:

    # c "Apparently so."
    c "확실히 그렇죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:905
translate Korean wrong2_7c631ae3:

    # An "No. You see, it's a trick question. Three is the correct answer, because that's the number that you took away."
    An "아니에요. 그건 함정이었어요. 세 개가 맞아요. \"당신\"에게 몇 개가 남았느냐는 질문이었으니까."

# game/anna1.rpy:911
translate Korean wrong2_f1b4da89:

    # An "Not like mine was any better, but I still knew the answer."
    An "제 것 처럼 나은 질문은 아니었기도 했고, 전 정답도 알고 있었죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:912
translate Korean wrong2_6abca927:

    # c "Oh well."
    c "아."

# game/anna1.rpy:917
translate Korean wrong2_10d76594:

    # An "As you wish."
    An "원하시는대로요."

# game/anna1.rpy:923
translate Korean wrong2_43eb0a75:

    # An "Don't be so childish."
    An "어린애처럼 굴지 말자구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:924
translate Korean wrong2_a349b77c:

    # c "Alright, alright."
    c "알았어요, 알았어."

# game/anna1.rpy:932
translate Korean cont2_65920a5b:

    # c "Okay, here's your question: In which year of our timeline did we gain sentience?"
    c "그럼, 당신의 질문은... 우리에게 지각력이 생긴 때는 몇 년도인가?"

# game/anna1.rpy:933
translate Korean cont2_5792ac54:

    # An "Zero. The beginning of our timeline marks the event when we gained sentience."
    An "0년. 지각력이 생겼을 때 부터 역사를 기록했기 때문이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:934
translate Korean cont2_735eded7:

    # c "Right again. Have you played this game before?"
    c "또 맞았네요. 이 게임 해보셨나봐요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:938
translate Korean cont2_de3d5afd:

    # An "It's a children's game. These questions aren't really a challenge."
    An "어린애들의 게임이잖아요. 도전조차도 못 되겠는데요."

# game/anna1.rpy:942
translate Korean cont2_b5ffa71d:

    # An "I'll just go ahead and draw the next card, so we can end this."
    An "다음 카드를 뽑아서 끝내야겠네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:962
translate Korean cont2_ecaa91ea:

    # An "An adventurer who values his life has to choose between three rooms to cross. Which one of the following would be the safest?"
    An "자신의 생명을 소중히 여기는 한 모험가가 있다. 그는 세 개의 방 중 한 곳을 지나쳐야 하는데, 어떤 방이 지나가기에 가장 안전하겠는가?"

# game/anna1.rpy:963
translate Korean cont2_ac54beca:

    # An "#1: A room filled with poisonous gas. #2: A room filled with one hundred highly trained assassins. #3: A room submerged in water filled with alligators that have not eaten in eight months."
    An "#1: 독성 가스로 가득찬 방. #2: 100명의 숙련된 암살자들이 있는 방. #3: 8달동안 먹지 않아 굶주린 악어들이 있는 방."

# game/anna1.rpy:978
translate Korean cont2_e0e6802f:

    # An "That's right. All the rooms are equally deadly. Alligators can go up to two years or more without food, making room #3 as deadly as the others. The other two rooms should not require any explanation."
    An "맞아요. 모두들 위험하죠. 악어들은 음식이 없어도 2년까지 버틸 수 있죠. 다른 두 방은 말할 것도 없이 위험하구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:982
translate Korean cont2_2fe75ba3:

    # An "At least according to this card. To be honest, I think the answer is debatable."
    An "적어도 이 카드에 적혀진 바에 따르면요. 솔직히, 논란의 여지가 있는 정답이네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:983
translate Korean cont2_eda2a1fe:

    # An "Don't worry, I'll still count it as a right answer for you. No need to get your tail caught in a door about it."
    An "걱정 마세요, 한 점 딴 걸로 쳐드릴테니. 굳이 이런 것에 물고늘어질 필요는 없죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:989
translate Korean wrong3_4100da8d:

    # An "Nope. In fact, all the rooms are equally deadly. Alligators can go up to two years or more without food, making room #3 as deadly as the others. The other two rooms should not require any explanation."
    An "아뇨. 사실, 모든 방이 위험해요. 악어들은 음식이 없어도 2년까지 버틸 수 있어요. 따라서 3번 방도 다른 방들처럼 위험하죠. 다른 방들이야 뭐, 설명할 필요도 없고요."

# game/anna1.rpy:992
translate Korean wrong3_76d7a50c:

    # An "Don't blame me. I didn't make this game."
    An "절 탓하지 마세요. 이 게임을 만든 건 제가 아니니까."

# game/anna1.rpy:998
translate Korean wrong3_a3dabf65:

    # An "Guess you don't like this game so much anymore."
    An "이 게임을 더 이상 좋아하지 않으시나 보네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1004
translate Korean wrong3_a083c857:

    # An "I do. I think you're about to lose."
    An "전 알겠는데요. 곧 패배하실 것 같네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1009
translate Korean cont4_cfde30fd:

    # c "Looks like this is going to be the last question."
    c "이게 마지막 질문인 것 같군요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1013
translate Korean cont4_58cb19cf:

    # An "Just get it over with already."
    An "그냥 빨리 끝내버리죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:1018
translate Korean cont4_f883752b:

    # c "What is the approximate acceleration speed of a nosediving flyer?"
    c "급강하하는 플라이어(flyer)의 정확한 가속도는?"

# game/anna1.rpy:1022
translate Korean cont4_d35e2a23:

    # An "I'll have to think about that one for a minute."
    An "조금 생각해봐야겠네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1023
translate Korean cont4_d19f855d:

    # c "..."
    c "..."

# game/anna1.rpy:1024
translate Korean cont4_cf49fd2e:

    # c "I was just kidding."
    c "그냥 농담이에요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1028
translate Korean cont4_a1c6efd2:

    # An "I still could have calculated that."
    An "그래도 전 계산할 수 있어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1029
translate Korean cont4_5879abc9:

    # c "Okay, here's the real question: What is the only substance known to be lighter in its solid form compared to its liquid state?"
    c "그러면 진짜 질문 갑니다. 액체 상태에 비해 고체 상태에서 가벼운 것으로 알려진 유일한 물질은?"

# game/anna1.rpy:1030
translate Korean cont4_f229ea8c:

    # An "Water."
    An "물."

# game/anna1.rpy:1031
translate Korean cont4_c9ea376e:

    # c "That seems to be correct."
    c "맞네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1035
translate Korean cont4_dccf5e6d:

    # An "Of course it is, duh!"
    An "당연히 맞겠죠!"

# game/anna1.rpy:1056
translate Korean cont4_0bc70d2b:

    # s "You answered Anna's questions correctly!"
    s "당신은 안나의 질문에 모두 정확히 답했습니다!"

# game/anna1.rpy:1060
translate Korean cont4_181cb589:

    # s "You answered Anna's questions correctly. Well done."
    s "당신은 안나의 질문에 모두 정확히 답했습니다. 잘하셨어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1064
translate Korean cont4_69150ed7:

    # s "You answered Anna's questions correctly. Feel free to imagine a celebratory rain of confetti pouring down on you, if that makes you feel good."
    s "당신은 안나의 질문에 모두 정확히 답했습니다. 쏟아지는 축하 향연을 상상해보세요. 그게 당신을 기분을 좋게 한다면."

# game/anna1.rpy:1067
translate Korean cont4_24197b9f:

    # An "Well, it appears to me that our game has ended in a tie."
    An "음, 무승부로 끝나버린 것 같네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1068
translate Korean cont4_a41b1b4e:

    # c "What do you propose?"
    c "뭐 제안하실 거라도 있으세요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:1070
translate Korean cont4_3e4449d6:

    # An "I say we both get our rewards. After all, we each made a good effort to get them."
    An "양 쪽 모두 보상을 받는 건 어때요? 사실, 우리가 서로 노력을 했잖아요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1071
translate Korean cont4_3291805c:

    # c "That's fine with me."
    c "전 괜찮을 것 같아요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1073
translate Korean cont4_6238581e:

    # An "I won't have a spot in the facility to do the tests for a while, though, so I suppose next time we meet, it'll be a date."
    An "당분간은 마땅히 실험할 장소가 없을 것 같아요. 그래서 다음에 만나면 그게 데이트가 되겠죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:1074
translate Korean cont4_af0d0955:

    # c "Don't forget what I said earlier about what I expect from you on this date. You better be on your best behavior."
    c "다음 데이트에 당신이 뭘 해야할 지 잊지 마세요. 당신은 최선을 다 해야할 거에요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1076
translate Korean cont4_ba35d478:

    # An "I'll try."
    An "노력해보죠."

