translate Korean cont4_27a8acdb:

    # n "Despite all odds, I managed to match her perfect score in the game we played."
    n "온갖 고난에도 불구하고, 나는 우리가 헀던 게임에서 완벽한 점수를 받아내고야 말았다."

# game/anna1.rpy:1093
translate Korean cont4_4e513385:

    # n "Even though my bet of forcing her to go on a proper date with me was more to get back at her for her earlier rudeness, I had not expected this outcome. I was not even sure what I expected from this meeting in the first place, but now I was locked into going on a date with her and being her own, personal guinea pig."
    n "비록 내가 먼저 그녀가 무례하게 굴었다는 이유 하나만으로 홧김에 제안한 데이트였지만, 결과가 이렇게 되리란 건 상상조차 하지 못했다. 처음부터 이 만남으로부터 뭘 얻을 수 있을 지 가늠도 하지 못했지만, 아무튼 지금은 그녀와 데이트를 하고, 그녀의 개인적인 프로젝트를 위한 실험 대상이 되기로 했다."

# game/anna1.rpy:1094
translate Korean cont4_7f2e72b6:

    # n "Whether anything good would come of this, I wasn't sure, either."
    n "어떤 이득이 있을지 조차 나는 확신할 수 없었다."

# game/anna1.rpy:1123
translate Korean anna1skip_e7d90bc0:

    # An "Just look at that, I won."
    An "보아하니, 제가 이겼네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1124
translate Korean anna1skip_4a4ac067:

    # c "Someone had to."
    c "누군가는 이겨야하니까요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1126
translate Korean anna1skip_b1004111:

    # An "This turned out to be more fun than I expected. Of course, the main reason for that is because I won, but still..."
    An "제가 예상한 것보다 재밌긴 하네요. 물론, 재밌었던 이유는 제가 이겼기 때문이었겠지만, 뭐 그래도..."

# game/anna1.rpy:1127
translate Korean anna1skip_f3e7a485:

    # c "I get it. You won, you're great, et cetera."
    c "알았어요. 당신이 이겼고, 당신은 최고고, 뭐 기타 등등."

# game/anna1.rpy:1129
translate Korean anna1skip_e0c94576:

    # An "That is true."
    An "그건 사실이죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:1130
translate Korean anna1skip_65d81ac2:

    # c "So, when should I come in for the tests?"
    c "그래서, 제가 언제쯤 실험하러 갈까요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:1132
translate Korean anna1skip_ee815ce8:

    # An "Actually, I'm not sure if I'll get a spot for them in the facility anytime soon, but I'll be sure to let you know."
    An "사실, 시설에 마땅한 자리가 있는지 확실하지 않아서요. 곧 알려드릴게요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1133
translate Korean anna1skip_0a6adcc2:

    # c "I'm quite sure you will."
    c "그럴 거라고 확신하죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:1135
translate Korean anna1skip_591c3b68:

    # An "But you know what, this wasn't so bad after all. Maybe I'll let you have your date."
    An "하지만 그거 아세요? 이거 은근히 괜찮았어요. 제가 데이트 정도는 해드릴 수 있을 것 같은데."

# game/anna1.rpy:1136
translate Korean anna1skip_4e24c2ca:

    # c "Really?"
    c "정말요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:1137
translate Korean anna1skip_f5f06e56:

    # An "Sure. I mean, you didn't win, but I think you earned it nonetheless. Or maybe I'm just that nice."
    An "물론이죠. 그러니까, 당신이 이기지는 않았지만, 그럴 만한 자격은 있으신 것 같네요. 아니면 그냥 제가 착한거거나."

# game/anna1.rpy:1138
translate Korean anna1skip_fe5f3366:

    # c "Okay."
    c "알았어요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1139
translate Korean anna1skip_2318ff16:

    # An "Well, it's up to you. Call me if you're interested."
    An "뭐, 그 쪽 마음대로 하세요. 관심있으시면 연락주시고."

# game/anna1.rpy:1140
translate Korean anna1skip_79abe5b9:

    # c "I'll let you know."
    c "곧 연락드리죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:1142
translate Korean anna1skip_f8eae38a:

    # An "I'm still going to collect my prize, though."
    An "물론 제가 이겼으니 전리품은 챙길거구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1143
translate Korean anna1skip_bae7468d:

    # c "I'm sure you'll make sure of that."
    c "그건 확실히 하시겠네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1145
translate Korean anna1skip_b9e3523e:

    # An "You bet I will. In any case, I should get going now. My \"break\" is just about to end. Bye!"
    An "당연하죠. 아무튼, 지금은 가봐야겠네요. 제 \"휴식\" 시간이 이제 막 끝나서요. 그럼 안녕!"

# game/anna1.rpy:1150
translate Korean anna1skip_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/anna1.rpy:1153
translate Korean anna1skip_4190e1e7:

    # n "I was not sure what I had expected out of this encounter, but it certainly wasn't this."
    n "이 만남에서 내가 뭘 기대했는 지는 모르겠지만, 확실히 이건 아니었다."

# game/anna1.rpy:1154
translate Korean anna1skip_6329633b:

    # n "After all, proposing a proper date was my way of sticking it to her for being rude."
    n "결국, 적절한 데이트를 제안한 건 그녀에게 무례하다고 눈치를 주기 위해서였다."

# game/anna1.rpy:1155
translate Korean anna1skip_1935d8cf:

    # n "Even though I lost the bet, she didn't seem to mind going on a date with me, as long as she got what she wanted. Whether I would follow up on it was up to me, though."
    n "물론 내가 내기를 지긴 했지만, 그녀가 원하는 걸 얻어가기만 한다면 나와 데이트를 하는 걸 꺼려해하지는 않은 것 같다. 물론 그 일을 할 지는 내게 달려있었다."

# game/anna1.rpy:1182
translate Korean anna1skip_5a69d41d:

    # An "And in a twist of fate that shocked no one, Anna, the magnificent, won the game."
    An "그리고 충격적인 반전 따위는 없이, 위대한 안나가 승리했네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1183
translate Korean anna1skip_73914479:

    # c "Oh, knock it off."
    c "아, 그만하세요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1185
translate Korean anna1skip_840cf566:

    # An "What's your problem? I earned this."
    An "뭐가 문제신데요? 제가 이겼다구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1186
translate Korean anna1skip_51af90a0:

    # c "I suppose you did, but you had the home field advantage."
    c "확실히 그렇긴 하지만, 당신은 홈그라운드 어드밴티지가 있잖아요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1188
translate Korean anna1skip_86f05589:

    # An "You didn't mind that when you proposed we play this stupid game. You're such a sore loser, you know that?"
    An "이 게임을 하자고 제안했을 때는 신경도 안 쓰셨으면서. 깨끗하게 인정하지 못하는 사람이시군요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1189
translate Korean anna1skip_7eb6d8f6:

    # c "And you're about the worst winner I've ever met."
    c "그러는 당신은 제가 만났던 우승자들 중 최악이시고요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1191
translate Korean anna1skip_35135016:

    # An "I think you're just experiencing acute posterior pain, because you don't get to go on a date with me now."
    An "제 생각엔 그냥 저랑 데이트할 수 없기 때문에 급성 후두통을 겪고 계신 것 같네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1192
translate Korean anna1skip_6af3e46d:

    # c "I didn't want to go on a date with you in the first place. I just wanted to teach you some manners."
    c "애초에 당신과 데이트할 생각은 추호에도 없었어요. 몇 가지 예절이나 좀 가르쳐주고 싶었을 뿐이었다고요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1194
translate Korean anna1skip_bba286a8:

    # An "Mission accomplished."
    An "미션 실패!"

# game/anna1.rpy:1195
translate Korean anna1skip_f64a830d:

    # c "See, that's what I'm talking about."
    c "보세요, 바로 그 태도가 제가 말하고자 하는 거라구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1197
translate Korean anna1skip_44223133:

    # An "Because you'd obviously be such a good teacher, the way you exude virtues such as civility and humbleness, and tried to force someone to go on a date with you on a bet."
    An "정중하고 겸손한 그 미덕을 보아하니 확실히 훌륭한 선생님이 되시겠네요. 누군가에게 내기로 데이트를 강제하려 하다니."

# game/anna1.rpy:1198
translate Korean anna1skip_0eabec36:

    # c "Maybe you should step down from your high horse for once."
    c "어쩌면 한 번은 거만하게 굴지 마시고 한 발 물러서는 것도 좋겠죠."

# game/anna1.rpy:1200
translate Korean anna1skip_b7bca3d1:

    # An "You criticize me, but you're such a hypocrite. I can't even understand what you're saying. What's a horse?"
    An "당신이 절 비판하고는 있지만, 당신은 위선자에 불과해요. 뭐라 말씀하시는 건지도 잘 모르겠네요. 한 발 물러서라니, 그건 또 뭔 소리에요?"

# game/anna1.rpy:1201
translate Korean anna1skip_089d2a2e:

    # c "There's no reasoning with you."
    c "당신에게 논리라곤 찾아볼 수 없군요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1202
translate Korean anna1skip_b8212a9e:

    # An "No, not since one of us thought they were somehow better than the other. Where did the sudden superiority complex come from?"
    An "아뇨, 우리 중 하나가 상대보다 더 나을거란 우월감을 가진 이후로부턴 아니죠. 그 콤플렉스는 도대체 어디서 튀어나온겁니까?"

# game/anna1.rpy:1203
translate Korean anna1skip_9ceffd57:

    # An "Just because, oh my gosh, you happen to be human and therefore deserve special treatment? You're just like Reza in that regard."
    An "그냥 말이죠, 세상에나, 당신이 인간이라서 뭐 특별 대우를 받길 원한거에요? 레자와 다를 바가 없네요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1204
translate Korean anna1skip_fc5368ed:

    # c "Reza..."
    c "레자..."

# game/anna1.rpy:1206
translate Korean anna1skip_fee6d309:

    # An "You know what? I'm leaving now, but don't expect for a minute that I won't make sure that you'll deliver on your end of the deal."
    An "그거 아세요? 이제 가봐야겠네요. 제가 거래를 끝마치지 않을 거라 함부로 넘겨짚지 마시구요."

# game/anna1.rpy:1207
translate Korean anna1skip_54119fe9:

    # c "Whatever."
    c "그러거나 말거나."

